                        "type":"info",
                        "instrux":"<p>Once you've clicked OK, the Payment Event Add popup will close, and take you to the Payment Event screen for the payment you just created.</p><p>Here, you can see the Amount Tendered and any Cash Back (change) the customer is owed. In this case, you would give Sophia $50 in change.</p>",
